task.summary: Correct settings, chess library working, start of UCI support.
Correctly working interface, along with support for playing two chess engines against each other.
Added a way to estimate the ELO rating of a chess engine by having it solve puzzles. Will be used to set appropriate difficulty during machine learning.
Added VERY simple AI, using the minimax search, and a VERY simple table-based evaluation function. It took 90 minutes to estimate the ELO, and only got 330.
Added alpha-beta pruning to AI, with MASSIVE timing improvement. Elo: 330. Time: 1m2.7s
Added better interface, kacce vs kacce or kace vs stockfish games, and the ability to save games, and open and view saved games.
